  'SMM Panel Payment Gateways: A Complete Guide',
  'smm-panel-payment-gateways-guide',
  '<h2>Payment Gateways for SMM Panels</h2><p>Offering multiple payment options is essential for maximizing your SMM panel revenue. The more payment methods you support, the more customers you can serve worldwide.</p><h2>Types of Payment Gateways</h2><h3>Traditional Gateways</h3><ul><li><strong>Stripe:</strong> Credit/debit cards, available in 40+ countries</li><li><strong>PayPal:</strong> The most widely recognized online payment method</li><li><strong>Razorpay:</strong> Popular in India for UPI, cards, and net banking</li></ul><h3>African Payment Gateways</h3><ul><li><strong>Flutterwave:</strong> Mobile money, cards, and bank transfers across Africa</li><li><strong>Paystack:</strong> Leading payment gateway in Nigeria and Ghana</li><li><strong>Korapay:</strong> Multi-currency payments for African businesses</li></ul><h3>Cryptocurrency Gateways</h3><ul><li><strong>Cryptomus:</strong> Accept Bitcoin, USDT, ETH, and 50+ cryptocurrencies</li><li><strong>CoinGate:</strong> Bitcoin and altcoin payments with fiat settlement</li><li><strong>Binance Pay:</strong> Direct crypto payments via Binance</li></ul><h2>HOME OF SMM Payment Integration</h2><p>HOME OF SMM supports 200+ payment gateways out of the box. Panel owners can enable/disable gateways through their dashboard — no coding required. Each gateway is fully configurable with custom API keys and settings.</p>',
